**BIG UPDATE**
Welcome to MocaDeco 3.0!
We're so excited to finally release the advanced version of MocaDeco.

• New logo, new icon, new user interface, new features.
• New 12 infrared filters.
• New 15 retro filters.
• New 7 antique filters.
• Hue and grain adjustments.
• Custom color & textures that can be applied to text, decos and canvas
• Camera composition guide.
• Bug fixes & performance improvements.

Love MocaDeco? Please give us a review!
We read every comment and review. Your thoughts and suggestions are taken into serious consideration as we continue to evolve MocaDeco.

New Tool
• HSL : The HSL tool gives you control to adjust the Hue, Saturation and Lightness of a specific color in the image.
If you select one of 8 colors, you can fine-tune that color without affecting other colors in the image.

New Filter
• 12 Neo Seoul Filters : Take a back street filed with neon signs and Inject a cyberpunk flavor.
